<br>
It saves time (don't have to run off to pull again), mana (if you're pacifying, most mobs eat up more than one paci unless you're killing REALLY fast), and gives your chanter and/or necro the opportunity to mana drain mezzed caster mobs to replenish their (or, in the necro's case, the group's) mana supply.<br>
<br>
